usted arregló

00:36:40.840 --> 00:36:42.960
una buena ceremonia.

00:36:44.000 --> 00:36:45.720
El nuevo rey asciende,

00:36:45.880 --> 00:36:47.640
demostrando su poder.

00:36:55.480 --> 00:36:56.440
cang xuan,

00:36:58.640 --> 00:36:59.480
ven aquí.

